data.description: Welcome to this delightful, character-filled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom older home with endless potential. Nestled in a quiet, established neighborhood, this property exudes timeless charm and offers a unique opportunity for those with a vision to restore and personalize their dream home. Sold as is, this property is perfect for DIY enthusiasts, investors, or anyone looking to add their personal touch to a classic residence. Seller says "bring an offer"...
